---
title: "Coach Roleplay - Multi-Turn Loop with Durable Execution"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ParseRequest: Rep sends /coach roleplay
    ParseRequest --> LoadProfile: Load rep skill profile
    LoadProfile --> RAGRetrieval: Pull ICP, objections, battle cards

    RAGRetrieval --> GeneratePersona: Create buyer persona
    GeneratePersona --> BuyerResponse: Generate buyer opening

    BuyerResponse --> SendToSlack: Post in Slack thread
    SendToSlack --> WaitForReply: DURABLE PAUSE

    note right of WaitForReply
        Graph state persisted to Postgres.
        Can resume hours/days later.
        Slack thread_ts = graph thread_id.
    end note

    WaitForReply --> ScoreRepTurn: Rep replies in thread
    ScoreRepTurn --> CheckTurns: More turns needed?

    CheckTurns --> BuyerResponse: Yes - continue roleplay
    CheckTurns --> GenerateDebrief: No - end roleplay

    GenerateDebrief --> UpdateProfile: Save scores to rep profile
    UpdateProfile --> FormatSlack: Post debrief in thread
    FormatSlack --> [*]
